{"word":"G4758 - στρατολογέω - stratologéō - strat-ol-og-eh'-o - Choose to be a soldier","slug":"G4758","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στρατολογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>stratologéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>strat-ol-og-eh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Choose to be a soldier"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03C1;&#x03B1;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - stratologeo&#x0304;</b> - <i>strat-ol-og-eh'-o</i><p/>From a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G4756\">G4756</a> and <a href=\"#/G3004\">G3004</a> (in its original sense); to <i>gather</i> (or <i>select</i>) as a <i>warrior</i>, that is, <i>enlist</i> in the army: - choose to be a soldier."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G4752\">G4752</a>, <a href=\"#/G4753\">G4753</a>, <a href=\"#/G4754\">G4754</a>, <a href=\"#/G4755\">G4755</a>, <a href=\"#/G4756\">G4756</a>, <a href=\"#/G4757\">G4757</a>, <a href=\"#/G4759\">G4759</a>, <a href=\"#/G4760\">G4760</a>"}]}